import React from 'react'
import {Card,CardImg,CardTitle,CardText,CardBody} from 'reactstrap'


const About = () => {
        return(
            <Card>
                <CardImg src="/images/siva1.jpg" width="40%" alt="SIVA" />
                <CardBody>
                    <CardTitle>About Me</CardTitle>
                    <CardText>I am Sivaraman</CardText>
                    <CardText>I am a enthusiastic and self-motivated person looking for a career opportunity to expand my
                     learnings, knowledge, and skills, while making a significant contribution to the success of the company</CardText>
                     <CardText>I am a final year student pursuing my under graduation in Computer Science and Engineering from Kumaraguru College of Technology</CardText>
                </CardBody>
            </Card>
            
        )
    
}

export default About
